      • flat

        public EntityProperty<V> flat()

        Create new "flat" property for toMany relationship.

        Example: 

        
 List<Object[]> result = ObjectSelect
      .columnQuery(Artist.class, Artist.ARTIST_NAME, Artist.PAINTING_ARRAY.flat())
      .select(context);
